description	"Kyle Katarn

^2Weaponry:
- Kyle's Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red / Blue Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense   (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (3)
- Push  (3)
- Pull  (3)
- Sense (3)
- Speed (3)
- Grip  (3)

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

After Desann's defeat, Kyle kept his lightsaber and continued in the ways of the Force as an instructor and Jedi Master at Luke's Academy. Kyle took on two students, Jaden Korr and Rosh Penin to train in the ways of the Jedi. Both students were talented, progressing quickly under Kyle's tutelage."